[32m│[0m ## Critical Security Discovery                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Identified**: Authorization bypass via manipulated user_id   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m parameter                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
